Package fms_server.dao

Interface IDatabaseAccessObject<T,V>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - This is the type of the IDatabaseAccessObject
    V - This is the type of the identifier, can be Integer or String
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    EventDAO, PersonDAO, UserDAO
    public interface IDatabaseAccessObject<T,V>
    This is the Data Access Object interface, gives a simple interface to be used with all IDatabaseAccessObject's
